author: National Geographic
description:
Ride along with officers attempting to stop smugglers throughout the United States in this To Catch a Smuggler MEGA episode. Featuring three full episodes: 

Weed in, Weed Out
Border Patrol scans the interstate for smugglers and stops a suspect who flees arrest. CBP seizes large amounts of inbound and outbound marijuana.

Cocaine Rides in the Crew Cab
HSI runs a human trafficking sting at a KC hotel. CBP in Philly is on the hunt for a passenger suspected of making terroristic threats in the US.  

Boatloads of Coke
CBP finds an SUV loaded with meth at the border and counterfeit cash in Atlanta. Operation Blood Moon yields 2000 kilos of cocaine in Puerto Rico.
